      "html": "<p block-type=\"Text\">In the limit of constant volatility, Merton [5] provided the first analytical formula for a down-and-out call option. Later on, Reiner and Rubinstein [6] extended the formula for all eight combinations of barriers (<i>see</i> <b>Pricing Formulae for Foreign Exchange Options</b>).</p>",
