    {
      "id": "/page/2/Text/6",
      "block_type": "Text",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"Text\" class=\"has-continuation\">Often, the barrier option has a discrete barrier schedule but the exact valuation is only available for the case of continuous barrier. In the constant volatility</p>",
