      "html": "<p block-type=\"TextInlineMath\">case, Broadie <i>et al.</i> [1] proposed that, by adjusting the barrier level in the continuous barrier option valuation, one would obtain a good approximation of the discrete barrier option value. The adjustment to the barrier level is prescribed by the following formula:</p>",
